WEBVTT

00:10:59.403 --> 00:11:00.641
is growing fast

00:11:01.424 --> 00:11:05.938
as we all become aware of this monster
we have unleashed in our pocket.

00:11:06.684 --> 00:11:09.150
I'm a mother of two preteen girls,

00:11:09.174 --> 00:11:10.769
and trust me,

00:11:10.793 --> 00:11:15.988
the single biggest source of stress
and anxiety as a parent,

00:11:16.012 --> 00:11:19.776
for me, is my children's
relationship with technology.

00:11:21.161 --> 00:11:25.000
This is a three-page agreement
my husband and I make them sign

00:11:25.024 --> 00:11:27.301
before they receive
their first [mobile phone].

00:11:27.325 --> 00:11:28.993
(Laughter)

00:11:29.619 --> 00:11:31.937
We want to help them to become